Cannot be Knocked Down
Cannot be Mind Tricked
Cannot be Sensed

Abilities:
Uncanny Supernatural Speed (Force Speed 1)
Anti-Force Resilience (Absorb 2)
Flip Kick 2
Gun Bash

Weakness:
